title: 'Wastage of money'
body: I wish i could give a 0star rating but that's not possible so i gave a 1. Below are the reasons mentioned. I ordered this top in 2 colors, when i got them 1. The size was wrong it was too big. 2. Black one had a defect on the front. 3. Neckline is nothing like shown in the pictures. 4. I returned it and it's been almost 2 months and i haven't received the refund. Customer care people are telling that amazon have already returned the refund amount in the same month.i have checked my account history, got my passbook printed and checked in almost every way i can. Please do not buy this!!!!!

title: 'Really stylish and good for its price'
body: It looks really stylish as top. The material is very stretchy so u can buy one size less for body hugging look.This tshirt wont look good as loose so if u don't have curves it might not look good on you.But if you have hourglass kind of figure ,u gonna look bomb in this.it might look good on straight physique too but if you have apple body type,stay away from body hugging stretchy material. It is not cotton so not good for delhi summers but one can easily wear in places like banglore. Overall its a good purchase for the money.cutting and stitching is good .color black is lilttle faded not very bright. I am definitely going to buy more of it .and this brand is really cool if u have low budget.
